        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Representative thoracic vertebra of the Alligator hailensis holotype (UF 224688) in (clockwise from top left) anterior, posterior, right lateral, and left lateral views. Scale = 2 cm." ;
